# Content Review & Publication Workflow — Implementation Plan

## Goal

Implement a complete content lifecycle: **DRAFT → PENDING_REVIEW → APPROVED/REJECTED → Displayed on Mentor Profile**. This adds admin content moderation, an audit trail, and mentor-controlled profile content selection.

---

## Status Flow

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DRAFT : Mentor creates content
    DRAFT --> PENDING_REVIEW : Mentor submits for review
    PENDING_REVIEW --> APPROVED : Admin approves
    PENDING_REVIEW --> REJECTED : Admin rejects (with reason)
    REJECTED --> DRAFT : Mentor revises & re-edits
    APPROVED --> DRAFT : Mentor unpublishes
    DRAFT --> ARCHIVED : Mentor archives
    APPROVED --> ARCHIVED : Mentor archives
    ARCHIVED --> APPROVED : Mentor restores (was approved, flag=false)
    ARCHIVED --> DRAFT : Mentor restores (was not approved, or flag=true)
```

Only **APPROVED** content is eligible for display on the mentor's public profile.

