### 2. API Routes

#### [NEW] `app/api/mentors/content/[id]/submit-review/route.ts`

**POST** — Mentor submits content for admin review.

- Auth: `requireMentor()`
- Validates: content exists, belongs to mentor, status is `DRAFT` or `REJECTED`
- Updates: `status → PENDING_REVIEW`, `submittedForReviewAt → now()`
- Creates audit log: `action = 'SUBMITTED'`
- Returns: updated content

---

#### [NEW] `app/api/admin/content/route.ts`

**GET** — Admin fetches all content with filtering.

- Auth: [ensureAdmin()](file:///c:/Users/Admin/young-minds-landing-page/app/api/admin/mentors/%5BmentorId%5D/audit/route.ts#9-32)
- Query params: `?status=PENDING_REVIEW&mentorId=xxx&type=COURSE&page=1&limit=20`
- Returns: paginated list with mentor name, content title, type, status, submittedAt
- Joins `mentor_content` with `mentors` and `user` tables for display names/emails

---

#### [NEW] `app/api/admin/content/[id]/route.ts`

**GET** — Admin fetches single content detail (same deep fetch as mentor route, but no ownership check).

---

#### [NEW] `app/api/admin/content/[id]/review/route.ts`

**POST** — Admin approves or rejects content.

- Auth: [ensureAdmin()](file:///c:/Users/Admin/young-minds-landing-page/app/api/admin/mentors/%5BmentorId%5D/audit/route.ts#9-32)
- Body: `{ action: 'APPROVE' | 'REJECT', note?: string }`
- Validates: content exists, status is `PENDING_REVIEW`
- If APPROVE: `status → APPROVED`, `reviewedAt → now()`, `reviewedBy → adminUserId`
- If REJECT: `status → REJECTED`, `reviewedAt → now()`, `reviewedBy → adminUserId`, `reviewNote → note` (required for rejection)
- Creates audit log entry
- Returns: updated content

---

#### [NEW] `app/api/mentors/profile-content/route.ts`

**GET** — Returns the mentor's currently selected profile content (ordered).

**PUT** — Updates the mentor's profile content selection.
- Body: `{ contentIds: string[] }` — ordered array of content IDs
- Validates: all IDs belong to the mentor AND have `APPROVED` status
- Replaces existing `mentor_profile_content` rows (delete all + insert new)
- Returns: updated selection

---

#### [NEW] `app/api/mentors/[mentorId]/public-content/route.ts`

**GET** — Public endpoint (no auth required) for mentee-facing profile.
- Returns: approved + profile-selected content for a given mentor, ordered by `displayOrder`
- Only returns safe fields (title, description, type, category, tags, thumbnail — no internal IDs/URLs for unpublished items)

