## Decisions Made

- **Status**: Migrate `PUBLISHED` → `APPROVED`, drop `PUBLISHED` from enum
- **Profile**: Only wire up content section; do NOT touch existing hardcoded mock data
- **Archive/Restore**: `requireReviewAfterRestore` flag (default `false`). Restoring previously-approved content skips re-verification for now.

